 \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1330}, {\"ngram\": \"the last few years\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1352}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray underwent back surgery on a spinal cyst at the end of June, having initially been told he would not recover in time to play either at Wimbledon or in France, but an accelerated period of rehabilitation saw him fit enough to play doubles at both events.\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1639, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1537, \"end\": 1543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8640433656420952, \"rank\": 0.15732832392154258, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Murray\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1386}, {\"ngram\": \"back surgery\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1409}, {\"ngram\": \"a spinal cyst\", \"from\": 1413, \"to\": 1426}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1437}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1445}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1498, \"to\": 1502}, {\"ngram\": \"Wimbledon\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1530}, {\"ngram\": \"an accelerated period\", \"from\": 1549, \"to\": 1570}, {\"ngram\": \"rehabilitation\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1588}, {\"ngram\": \"doubles\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1623}, {\"ngram\": \"both events\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1638}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was, however, forced to pull out of the singles at both tournaments and says his latest comeback from injury convinced him that the time is right to walk away from the game.\", \"from\": 1641, \"to\": 1817, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the singles\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1691}, {\"ngram\": \"both tournaments\", \"from\": 1695, \"to\": 1711}, {\"ngram\": \"his latest comeback\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1740}, {\"ngram\": \"injury\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1752}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1780}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1816}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was told that if the cyst continues to grow and puts more pressure on the nerves, it turns into an emergency situation where you can not control your bladder and you will lose control of the other leg,\\\" he explained.\", \"from\": 1819, \"to\": 2038, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the cyst\", \"from\": 1839, \"to\": 1847}, {\"ngram\": \"more pressure\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1888}, {\"ngram\": \"the nerves\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 1902}, {\"ngram\": \"an emergency situation\", \"from\": 1918, \"to\": 1940}, {\"ngram\": \"your bladder\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1979}, {\"ngram\": \"control\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2005}, {\"ngram\": \"the other leg\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2022}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's kind of when I knew it was time.\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2079, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2078}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been really hard.\", \"from\": 2081, \"to\": 2104, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Physically, pain-wise, I feel bad.\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2139, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's also why I am happy to be finishing, because if I kept going and kept trying, eventually you end up having an injury potentially ending your career.\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2295, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an injury\", \"from\": 2254, \"to\": 2263}, {\"ngram\": \"your career\", \"from\": 2283, \"to\": 2294}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, I know that now is the right time and physically, it's been really hard.\\\"\", \"from\": 2296, \"to\": 2373, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the right time\", \"from\": 2319, \"to\": 2333}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Andy Murray's My London: 'A good first date?\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2419, \"entities\": [{\"